Module 6: Level Of Detail (LOD) Expressions Tableau

Case Study II – Problem Statement

Problem Statement:
You’ve been hired by the Shire Oakmont a Stock Trading Company.
You’ve been appointed as their Sr. BI Analyst and your task is to visualize the Percentage of difference
from average value across a range of values.

The company wants you to compare their daily close value of a stock against the average daily close value and
show their difference in percent. To make things a little complicated the company has asked you to compare the results
across a selected time range.

The data has been provided to you and contains the following:
• Company Name
• Date
• Ticker
• Adj Close

Hint: In order to create this visualization you’ll need help of the following feature:
• Level Of Detail
• Calculated Field
• Parameters
